<span class="n">BOLSONARO</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">BOLSONARO</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">astype</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;int32&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">OUTROS</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">OUTROS</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">astype</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;int32&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">NULO</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">NULO</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">astype</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;int32&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">TOTAL</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">LULA</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">BOLSONARO</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">OUTROS</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">NULO</span>

<span class="c1"># inov = 0.025</span>
<span class="n">inov</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.035</span> <span class="c1"># 0.025</span>

<span class="k">with</span> <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Model</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">grw</span><span class="p">:</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># inov = pm.HalfNormal(&#39;inov&#39;, sigma=0.15)</span>

    <span class="n">grw_lula</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GaussianRandomWalk</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;lula&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">sd</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">inov</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">shape</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">n_days</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="n">grw_bolsonaro</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GaussianRandomWalk</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;bolsonaro&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">sd</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">inov</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">shape</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">n_days</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="n">grw_demais</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GaussianRandomWalk</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;demais&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">sd</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">inov</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">shape</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">n_days</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="n">grw_nulo</span>  <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">GaussianRandomWalk</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;nulo&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">sd</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">inov</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">shape</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">n_days</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="c1"># grw  = pm.GaussianRandomWalk(&#39;grw&#39;, mu=0, sd=inov, shape=(n_days, 3))</span>
    

    <span class="n">prob</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Deterministic</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;softmax&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">tt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">nnet</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">softmax</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">stack</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="n">grw_lula</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">poll_day</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">grw_bolsonaro</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">poll_day</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">grw_demais</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">poll_day</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="n">grw_nulo</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">poll_day</span><span class="p">]],</span> <span class="n">axis</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)))</span>
    <span class="c1"># prior = tt.nnet.softmax(grw[poll_day])</span>
    
    <span class="c1">#conc  = pm.Uniform(&quot;concentration&quot;, lower=50, upper=250)</span>
    <span class="n">conc</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Gamma</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;concentration&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">alpha</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">beta</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mf">0.075</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DirichletMultinomial</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;observed&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">n</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">TOTAL</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">prob</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">conc</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">observed</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="n">LULA</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">values</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">BOLSONARO</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">values</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">OUTROS</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">values</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">NULO</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">values</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">T</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">shape</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">poll_day</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">))</span>
    
    <span class="n">trace</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sample</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1000</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">tune</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2000</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">progressbar</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">return_inferencedata</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">chains</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">cores</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">summary</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">az</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">summary</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">trace</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># used below</span>
    <span class="n">az</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">plot_trace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">trace</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">figsize</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">22</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">16</span><span class="p">))</span>  
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">datetime</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">now</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">strftime</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;%H:%M:%S&quot;</span><span class="p">))</span>
